channel.description: pretty sure it has been cache packaged and i am not sure how to use a cache editor so i would really like some help would be much appreciated

item.title: Anyone good client sided need someone to help me edit the cache to change login
item.dc:creator: @Roar337 Roar337
item.description:
@Roar337 wrote:

if you are trying to edit the picture that loads up when you open client i wouldn’t touch cache go into your client files and find the java that is responsible for loading the background and change it to use a picture in a folder where the cache is the old picture in the actual cache should simply be ignored and the client should load your background from wherever you told it to assuming windows isn’t whining about folder permissions again but that is a separate problem all together which you may or may not encounter.
